flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[pir_setup\nfan_setup\nload YOLO model]
    B --> C{smoke_timer\n> 30s?}

    C -->|Yes| D[smoke_check]
    D --> C2{smoke\ndetected?}
    C -->|No| C2

    C2 -->|Yes| E[close_window\nturn_off_fan\ninsert_sensor_reading_async]
    C2 -->|No| F{sensor_timer\n> 10s?}

    F -->|Yes| G[get_humTemp]
    G --> H{Reading\nvalid?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Update hum & temp]
    H -->|No| J[smart_print: fejl]
    I --> K[insert_sensor_reading_async]
    J --> K

    F -->|No| L[Fan control]
    K --> L

    L --> L1{temp >= 25\nand fan off?}
    L1 -->|Yes| L2[turn_on_fan]
    L1 -->|No| L3{temp < 25\nand fan on?}
    L3 -->|Yes| L4[turn_off_fan]
    L3 -->|No| L5[No action]

    L2 --> M[Window control]
    L4 --> M
    L5 --> M

    M --> M1{hum >= 60\nand window closed?}
    M1 -->|Yes| M2[open_window]
    M1 -->|No| M3{hum < 60\nand window open?}
    M3 -->|Yes| M4[close_window]
    M3 -->|No| M5[Forhold optimale]

    M2 --> N[read_pir]
    M4 --> N
    M5 --> N
    E --> N

    N --> O{Motion\ndetected?}

    O -->|No| P{Camera\nactive?}
    P -->|Yes| P1{motion_timer\n> 60s?}
    P1 -->|Yes| P2[kill_feed\ncamera_active = False]
    P1 -->|No| Q[sleep 0.5s]
    P -->|No| Q
    P2 --> Q

    O -->|Yes| R[Reset motion_timer]
    R --> S{Camera\nactive?}
    S -->|No| T[start_feed\ncamera_active = True]
    S -->|Yes| U{motion_timer\n< 60s?}
    T --> U

    U -->|Yes| V[get_processed_frame]
    V --> W{Frame\nvalid?}
    W -->|No| Q
    W -->|Yes| X[Run YOLO inference]
    X --> Y{YOLO\nresult?}

    Y -->|laying| Z[laying_frames ++\ncheck horse_down_counter]
    Y -->|standing| AA[Reset laying_frames\nhorse_was_laying = False]
    Y -->|None| AB[Ingen konklusion]

    Z --> Q
    AA --> Q
    AB --> Q

    U -->|No| AC[kill_feed\ncamera_active = False]
    AC --> Q

    Q --> C

    Q --> QA{Exception?}
    QA -->|KeyboardInterrupt| QB[Print: afbrudt]
    QA -->|Other| QC[Print: fejl]
    QB --> QD[close_camera\njanitor]
    QC --> QD
    QD --> QE([End])
